---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="About Cognara" description="Learn about Cognara's mission and approach" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>About Cognara</h1>
      
      <section>
        <h2>Core Identity</h2>
        <p>
          Cognara is a forward-thinking digital entity at the intersection of 
          Artificial Intelligence, storytelling, and educational media. We serve 
          as the foundational brand for a suite of AI-orchestrated projects.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Operational Philosophy</h2>
        <p>We operate as an "AI-Orchestrated Studio" defined by:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Efficiency:</strong> Reducing production time from hundreds of hours to less than 20 per episode</li>
          <li><strong>Quality:</strong> Maintaining documentary-grade aesthetics that compete with traditional media</li>
          <li><strong>Scalability:</strong> Building frameworks for consistent, rapid expansion into new niches</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>The Vision</h2>
        <p>
          Cognara proves that technology doesn't replace the creator: it acts as a 
          force multiplier for human imagination. We're building the future of the 
          creator economy.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p, li {
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  ul {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>